Grauer, Respondent, v. Grauer, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November 10, 1892.) Action by Grace Grauer against Frank Grauer.

Argued before Daly, C. J., and Bookstaver and Pryor, JJ.

No opinion. Order reversed, with costs, and with leave to appellant to apply for restitution. See 20 N. Y. Supp. 854.
